   "source": [
    "### standard normal distribution\n",
    "$$z=\\frac{X-\\mu}{\\sigma}$$\n",
    "$$f(z) = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2\\pi}} e^{-\\frac{z^2}{2}}$$\n",
    "$$\\mu:mean(average)$$\n",
    "$$\\sigma:std \\, dev(standard \\, deviation)$$\n",
    "$$X:some \\, data$$\n",
    "### get $\\sigma$\n",
    "$$\\sigma^2 = \\frac{\\sum ((x_n-\\mu)^2)}{N}$$\n",
    "$$\\sigma = \\sqrt{\\sigma^2}$$"
   ]
